ps and tongue, painful genital ulcers, and deep vein thrombophlebitis.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.16447,0.29367,0.082064,0.12025,0.074185,0.067051,0.05067,0.041364,0.033762,0.028438,0.02401,0.020069],"unified_progress":[0.18327,0.2035,0.098564,0.11453,0.084366,0.077559,0.058992,0.0504,0.042608,0.035571,0.029502,0.021132]},{"section":3,"text":"No urethritis or conjunctivitis.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.10817,0.18207,0.14383,0.095454,0.082859,0.086405,0.067123,0.068391,0.052683,0.044946,0.038126,0.02994],"unified_progress":[0.097513,0.13513,0.11944,0.10841,0.094815,0.093577,0.07745,0.077696,0.064141,0.055008,0.044725,0.032098]},{"section":4,"text":"Hmm.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.37257,0.063682,0.061896,0.067841,0.064373,0.05997,0.055398,0.057856,0.055891,0.050573,0.050865,0.039081],"unified_progress":[0.23872,0.10071,0.072173,0.066513,0.078922,0.072013,0.085428,0.073303,0.067527,0.053077,0.047619,0.043992]},{"section":5,"text":"First, the key symptoms here are the combination of oral and genital ulcers along with the leg swelling and DVT.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.082565,0.16407,0.074532,0.11126,0.095822,0.090826,0.077789,0.070353,0.064421,0.060686,0.056257,0.051419],"unified_progress":[0.086416,0.11821,0.07167,0.093542,0.093187,0.095608,0.087101,0.083707,0.078849,0.074302,0.066732,0.050675]},{"section":6,"text":"Aphthous ulcers are common, but when paired with genital ulcers and thrombosis, that's a red flag.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.053185,0.09895,0.11217,0.11076,0.1053,0.093998,0.088493,0.079982,0.071541,0.072626,0.058959,0.05403],"unified_progress":[0.050376,0.077516,0.091925,0.099267,0.099603,0.10021,0.096793,0.09204,0.086065,0.084847,0.06844,0.052915]},{"section":7,"text":"The absence of urethritis and conjunctivitis might rule out some conditions.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040643,0.084768,0.099615,0.10292,0.099792,0.094879,0.093231,0.088955,0.083592,0.082097,0.070856,0.058656],"unified_progress":[0.038327,0.072367,0.085736,0.094741,0.098821,0.097802,0.098125,0.097108,0.093176,0.09326,0.075445,0.055091]},{"section":8,"text":"I remember that Beh\u00e7et's disease is characterized by triad of oral ulcers, genital ulcers, and uveitis.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03416,0.069901,0.08411,0.098025,0.10634,0.10614,0.10506,0.096198,0.085205,0.085312,0.068948,0.0606],"unified_progress":[0.037088,0.058215,0.080139,0.091874,0.099583,0.11408,0.10572,0.10324,0.095958,0.089716,0.071313,0.053074]},{"section":9,"text":"But this patient doesn't have uveitis, though.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032876,0.070805,0.082324,0.088533,0.092462,0.096194,0.099789,0.10008,0.096825,0.09224,0.084017,0.063852],"unified_progress":[0.036595,0.065292,0.077555,0.08524,0.094413,0.096087,0.097997,0.10275,0.10049,0.10643,0.081522,0.055624]},{"section":10,"text":"Wait, but maybe the triad isn't always all three.","dimension":12,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029904,0.064398,0.079968,0.088757,0.09552,0.098164,0.10016,0.099374,0.096925,0.093175,0.083929,0.069724],"unified_progress":[0.055036,0.07133,0.080664,0.090219,0.09333,0.093643,0.10051,0.095772,0.091843,0.094297,0.077417,0.055941]},{"section":11,"text":"Beh\u00e7et's can have other manifestations like thrombophlebitis.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031748,0.065259,0.077894,0.090229,0.098678,0.10226,0.10403,0.098929,0.092317,0.091604,0.078009,0.069044],"unified_progress":[0.040529,0.060438,0.080451,0.089084,0.096374,0.10605,0.10191,0.10053,0.095817,0.091051,0.076254,0.061509]},{"section":12,"text":"The leg swelling could be due to DVT, which is a vascular issue.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025869,0.058855,0.073114,0.084968,0.094615,0.10061,0.10562,0.10231,0.099478,0.093343,0.087034,0.074184],"unified_progress":[0.045338,0.053044,0.065691,0.075638,0.08648,0.099106,0.097828,0.10031,0.10299,0.10119,0.095962,0.076418]},{"section":13,"text":"Beh\u00e7et's is known to cause both arterial and venous thrombosis.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030305,0.063547,0.076693,0.088016,0.095926,0.09987,0.10229,0.099001,0.094188,0.093458,0.08177,0.074934],"unified_progress":[0.039161,0.058022,0.073565,0.082196,0.090484,0.098315,0.10036,0.10098,0.099335,0.097055,0.087303,0.073232]},{"section":14,"text":"Another possibility is something like lupus, but lupus usually presents with malar rash, arthritis, maybe nephritis.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022708,0.055533,0.072345,0.084997,0.094147,0.09944,0.10625,0.10586,0.10206,0.10107,0.089475,0.066112],"unified_progress":[0.027384,0.0556,0.074454,0.084832,0.095203,0.10014,0.10371,0.10691,0.10443,0.10815,0.084663,0.054527]},{"section":15,"text":"The ulcers here are more suggestive of something else.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.02334,0.056791,0.073026,0.082867,0.089044,0.093741,0.1018,0.10455,0.10399,0.10349,0.095247,0.072107],"unified_progress":[0.029096,0.056094,0.071424,0.081563,0.091765,0.095166,0.10196,0.10673,0.10621,0.11298,0.089903,0.0571]},{"section":16,"text":"Then there's aphthous ulcers plus genital ulcers.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034152,0.066941,0.076618,0.085015,0.091755,0.095511,0.098113,0.097683,0.095872,0.095317,0.087176,0.075845],"unified_progress":[0.043029,0.061918,0.075832,0.08661,0.093215,0.10041,0.10151,0.10119,0.098901,0.094885,0.081571,0.060925]},{"section":17,"text":"Syphilis can cause genital ulcers, but usually not the oral ones as part of the primary stage.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024522,0.057582,0.073308,0.086839,0.096866,0.1021,0.10695,0.10398,0.098448,0.097899,0.08444,0.067069],"unified_progress":[0.030406,0.056528,0.0767,0.086722,0.096464,0.10457,0.10517,0.10597,0.10187,0.10053,0.079898,0.055174]},{"section":18,"text":"Also, syphilis wouldn't explain the DVT and leg swelling.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021134,0.05278,0.068385,0.079763,0.088542,0.096064,0.10526,0.10824,0.10747,0.10451,0.097458,0.070387],"unified_progress":[0.027257,0.054587,0.070551,0.079917,0.091934,0.096619,0.10137,0.1082,0.10785,0.11563,0.089961,0.05613]},{"section":19,"text":"Sarcoidosis can have oral ulcers and lymphadenopathy, but again, the DVT is a key point here.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.020038,0.050627,0.066544,0.078887,0.088444,0.095913,0.10524,0.10809,0.10766,0.10638,0.098449,0.073724],"unified_progress":[0.026403,0.053099,0.070306,0.081024,0.092285,0.098779,0.10333,0.10909,0.10865,0.11178,0.090299,0.054958]},{"section":20,"text":"The combination of mucocutaneous ulcers and thrombophlebitis makes me think of Beh\u00e7et's.","dimension":4,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028124,0.058144,0.070226,0.080902,0.089552,0.094961,0.099334,0.099126,0.099099,0.099897,0.094015,0.08662],"unified_progress":[0.037568,0.054675,0.069819,0.082102,0.090124,0.10001,0.10117,0.10226,0.1018,0.098554,0.089392,0.072521]},{"section":21,"text":"The deep vein thrombosis is a known vascular complication in Beh\u00e7et's.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025625,0.056034,0.069416,0.081326,0.091221,0.097742,0.10253,0.10076,0.098957,0.098077,0.091531,0.08678],"unified_progress":[0.034192,0.051857,0.065861,0.076003,0.085676,0.097378,0.098247,0.10146,0.10321,0.1023,0.097897,0.085915]},{"section":22,"text":"The absence of uveitis might mean that the patient hasn't developed that component yet, or it's just not present.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028988,0.062739,0.074242,0.082613,0.089717,0.096031,0.10016,0.10132,0.10041,0.097192,0.090199,0.076391],"unified_progress":[0.043019,0.065132,0.074083,0.081081,0.088566,0.092871,0.0955,0.099299,0.099141,0.10049,0.089718,0.071099]},{"section":23,"text":"The diagnostic criteria for Beh\u00e7et's include recurrent oral ulcers plus two of: genital ulcers, eye lesions, skin lesions, or positive pathergy test.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029501,0.063232,0.075178,0.086471,0.095502,0.10037,0.10336,0.10014,0.09454,0.093828,0.083067,0.07481],"unified_progress":[0.034747,0.058857,0.077943,0.086307,0.093492,0.10458,0.10186,0.10184,0.098402,0.094044,0.081764,0.066164]},{"section":24,"text":"Since he has oral and genital ulcers, that's two out of the four, so that's meeting criteria.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.037745,0.072919,0.082227,0.08796,0.091644,0.093905,0.095454,0.093937,0.091249,0.089675,0.082859,0.080425],"unified_progress":[0.051412,0.067956,0.077085,0.084354,0.089376,0.093069,0.092591,0.09424,0.092285,0.090418,0.08643,0.080783]},{"section":25,"text":"The DVT could be part of the vascular involvement, which is another extra criterion.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029655,0.062475,0.075671,0.085448,0.092514,0.096222,0.10024,0.097907,0.096707,0.09291,0.087792,0.082464],"unified_progress":[0.049902,0.057066,0.06938,0.077678,0.085588,0.09215,0.093421,0.09643,0.098241,0.098101,0.095555,0.086489]},{"section":26,"text":"Another thought: could it be a prothrombotic state?","dimension":0,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027898,0.059948,0.074731,0.084603,0.093785,0.097154,0.10125,0.10329,0.10095,0.098117,0.08924,0.069042],"unified_progress":[0.038159,0.067107,0.083194,0.094835,0.096765,0.097261,0.10045,0.098654,0.095699,0.092073,0.078223,0.057582]},{"section":27,"text":"But the ulcers don't fit there.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021278,0.052595,0.068724,0.079231,0.08876,0.094951,0.10371,0.10683,0.107,0.1042,0.098812,0.073913],"unified_progress":[0.036459,0.059142,0.073455,0.081806,0.093102,0.095503,0.099432,0.1053,0.10355,0.10631,0.08814,0.057808]},{"section":28,"text":"Maybe an inflammatory bowel disease?","dimension":0,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018192,0.049003,0.06699,0.079628,0.092624,0.09972,0.10579,0.11034,0.10862,0.1059,0.095774,0.067419],"unified_progress":[0.034649,0.065856,0.082863,0.09446,0.098418,0.099658,0.10311,0.1027,0.098375,0.094852,0.076154,0.048908]},{"section":29,"text":"But again, the ulcers and DVT are more Beh\u00e7et's.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018943,0.047719,0.063457,0.07468,0.085614,0.093449,0.10301,0.10742,0.10895,0.10779,0.10429,0.084674],"unified_progress":[0.029692,0.055636,0.070463,0.079451,0.090669,0.0955,0.099035,0.10535,0.10488,0.10759,0.093429,0.068305]},{"section":30,"text":"So putting it all together, Beh\u00e7et's disease is the most likely diagnosis here.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022494,0.043706,0.05343,0.061287,0.068774,0.075435,0.083215,0.089299,0.097306,0.104,0.11732,0.18374],"unified_progress":[0.025201,0.03318,0.041146,0.051155,0.056373,0.068435,0.074273,0.086157,0.095604,0.10719,0.14905,0.21223]}]}}